6
00:00:27,013 --> 00:00:29,730
Rachel: How the hell did
he survive Ruskov's ship?

7
00:00:29,766 --> 00:00:31,098
He managed to grab a life raft.

8
00:00:31,150 --> 00:00:32,733
Washed up on the Florida coast,

9
00:00:32,769 --> 00:00:34,769
