survivors took him in.

10
00:00:34,821 --> 00:00:38,105
I don't suppose he told
them that he was contagious.

11
00:00:38,107 --> 00:00:39,440
No.

12
00:00:39,492 --> 00:00:42,276
After that, he moved from camp
to camp, taking what he needed.

13
00:00:42,278 --> 00:00:44,578
It was either fate or bad luck
that led him to the immunes.

14
00:00:44,614 --> 00:00:47,615
And the labs? Did he lead
the Ramseys to Dr. Hunter?

15
00:00:47,667 --> 00:00:49,417
He wouldn't say.

16
00:00:49,452 --> 00:00:50,785
At least, not to me.

17
00:00:50,837 --> 00:00:53,337
[Sighs] So what are you gonna do with him?

18
00:00:53,373 --> 00:00:54,622
I haven't decided yet.

19
00:00:54,674 --> 00:00:57,258
And he only made one request.

20
00:00:57,293 --> 00:00:58,676
He wants to speak to you.

21
00:00:58,711 --> 00:01:00,211
No. It's not gonna happen.

22
00:01:00,263 --> 00:01:02,463
You said you were having
trouble nebulizing the vaccine.

23
00:01:02,515 --> 00:01:03,881
- Absolutely not.
- He started it.

24
00:01:03,933 --> 00:01:05,132
The primordial started it.

25
00:01:05,184 --> 00:01:06,884
He perpetuated it, weaponized it.

26
00:01:06,936 --> 00:01:08,135
I have his blood samples.

27
00:01:08,187 --> 00:01:09,854
Once I see what happens to the rats,

28
00:01:09,889 --> 00:01:11,772
I'll be able to find the
stability sequence he used

29
00:01:11,808 --> 00:01:13,891
to bind his D.N.A. to the virus.

30
00:01:13,943 --> 00:01:16,026
That will be the sum
total of his usefulness.

31
00:01:16,062 --> 00:01:17,812
You said that can take months.

32
00:01:17,864 --> 00:01:19,280
Captain...

33
00:01:19,315 --> 00:01:20,898
He killed my wife,

34
00:01:20,950 --> 00:01:25,069
and was able to talk to him.

35
00:01:25,121 --> 00:01:29,156
So unless you have a better idea...

36
00:01:31,627 --> 00:01:34,328
[Sighs]

37
00:01:34,330 --> 00:01:37,331
I know he's a snake,

38
00:01:37,383 --> 00:01:41,802
but if he can help,
you have to talk to him.

